  "title": "feat(chat): add top level components and templates",
  "body": "**Summary**\r\nThis PR adds top level component/template props to the chat widget that are then forwarded to their respective ui components. Support for replacing the entire `ChatHeader` and `ChatPrompt` component has also been added.\r\n\r\nTODO:\r\n- Remove props that would never get passed to custom header or prompt components (I believe these would be the element attributes)\r\n- Add support for toggle button components/layouts (can be done once some translations for it are added)",
